<p><label>REVEILLÉ</label>
(Fr. <hi rend="italic">réveillez,</hi> imperative of <hi rend="italic">réveiller,</hi> to awaken, Lat. <hi rend="italic">re-</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Vigilare,</hi> to watch), the signal by call of bugle or beat of drum to announce to soldiers the time to awake and begin duty.</p>
